itle=\"Locations\">Location</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Sorcerer%27s_Tower\" title=\"Sorcerer&#39;s Tower\">Sorcerer's Tower</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Choose_Option\" title=\"Choose Option\">Options</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">None</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">The scrying glass of a seer.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Map</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content infobox-image\"><a class=\"mw-kartographer-map mw-kartographer-container center\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 300px;background-image: url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/1_41_53.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/1_42_53.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/1_41_52.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/1_42_52.png); background-position: -158px -58px, 98px -58px, -158px 198px, 98px 198px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"300\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"3404\" data-lon=\"2701\" data-mapid=\"0\" data-plane=\"1\" data-overlays=\"[&quot;pins&quot;]\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/0/2/1/2701/3404\"></a></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"8\">Object ID</th><td colspan=\"12\">589</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<p>A <b>Crystal ball</b> is found on the table in the <a href=\"/w/Sorcerer%27s_Tower\" title=\"Sorcerer&#39;s Tower\">Sorcerer's Tower</a> on the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 2 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 1 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span>. It presumably belongs to the resident of the tower, <a href=\"/w/Thormac\" title=\"Thormac\">Thormac</a>.\n</p><p>When an item is used on the crystal ball, the message \"<i>The table appears to be in use.</i>\" appears in the chatbox, signifying that the crystal ball cannot be used as a <a href=\"/w/Table\" title=\"Table\">table</a>.<sup class=\"noprint fact\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text\" title=\"This fact is likely to be disputed and needs a source for confirmation.\">confirmation needed</span>&#93;</sup>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐7qtxl\nCached time: 20220420192013\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.096 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 102/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4704/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 44/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 812/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.035/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 887459/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   70.103      1 -total\n 82.17%   57.607      1 Template:Infobox_Scenery\n 22.18%   15.550      1 Template:Map\n  9.96%    6.979      1 Template:FloorNumber\n  7.37%    5.169      1 Template:Fact\n  2.77%    1.944      1 Template:Mainonly\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:328758-0!canonical and timestamp 20220420192013 and revision id 14144843. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{Infobox Scenery\n|name = Crystal ball\n|image = [[File:Crystal ball (Sorcerer&#39;s Tower).png|250x250px]]\n|release = <!-- Not present in RuneScape Classic -->\n|update = \n|members = Yes\n|quest = None\n|location = [[Sorcerer's Tower]]\n|options = None\n|examine = The scrying glass of a seer.\n|map = {{Map|x:2701,y:3404|plane=1|mapID=0|mtype=pin}}\n|id = 589\n}}\n\nA '''Crystal ball''' is found on the table in the [[Sorcerer's Tower]] on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}}. It presumably belongs to the resident of the tower, [[Thormac]].\n\nWhen an item is used on the crystal ball, the message \"''The table appears to be in use.''\" appears in the chatbox, signifying that the crystal ball cannot be used as a [[table]].{{fact}}"}